  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e3777ea8cdbcada889a03a",
      "text": "Samsung Browser(スマホアプリ)",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514946,
      "updated": 1776515091
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3778100000000009aebd0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514946,
      "updated": 1776515088
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3778100000000009aebd1",
      "text": "タブを99個までしか開けない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514946,
      "updated": 1776515112
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3778200000000009aebd2",
      "text": " 100個目を開こうとしたとき、一番古いタブを閉じようとしてくる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514947,
      "updated": 1776514976
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3778200000000009aebd3",
      "text": " タブが溜まらなくて済む",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514947,
      "updated": 1776515142
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3794000000000009aebe5",
      "text": "  大量に溜まったタブを処理する作業は疲れるし時間がかかって辛かいから、それが減って助かってる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776515392,
      "updated": 1776515492
    },
    {
      "id": "69e378ae00000000009aebdf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776515247,
      "updated": 1776515247
    },
    {
      "id": "69e377b000000000009aebd9",
      "text": "タブ数を忘れて使える",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514992,
      "updated": 1776515006
    },
    {
      "id": "69e377c400000000009aebdb",
      "text": " タブ数はタブビューを開くアイコンに書かれてる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776515013,
      "updated": 1776516516
    },
    {
      "id": "69e37db600000000000571bc",
      "text": " メニューのアイコンを並べ替える機能からタブビューを開くアイコンを非表示にすると、タブ数が見えなくなる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776516534,
      "updated": 1776516552
    },
    {
      "id": "69e398c80000000000edcea8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776523463,
      "updated": 1776523463
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3778200000000009aebd7",
      "text": "[ブラウザ]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776514947,
      "updated": 1776523463
    },
    {
      "id": "69e398c60000000000edcea7",
      "text": "[Samsung]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776523461,
      "updated": 1776523472
    },
